  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "German woman dies mysteriously",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Habaraduwa Police say that a German woman who was in a private house in Mataramba, Habaraduwa has died mysteriously inside the house.",
        "The deceased foreigner was a 60-year-old woman and she lived alone in this house.",
        "The police said that this German woman used to go to Germany from time to time and came back to this country and spent time in this house. It has been revealed in the police investigations that she had come to this country from Germany for the last time about two weeks ago.",
        "The post-mortem examination of the dead foreign woman's body is scheduled to be conducted today (20th) at the Galle Karapitiya Teaching Hospital."
      ],
